having your natural curiosity

00:31:03.000 --> 00:31:06.590
positively reinforced instead
of negatively reinforced.

00:31:06.590 --> 00:31:08.180
Kids are naturally curious.

00:31:08.180 --> 00:31:11.607
They don't have any
trouble asking questions.

00:31:11.607 --> 00:31:13.190
We slowly start doing
things that make

00:31:13.190 --> 00:31:15.090
people stop asking questions.

00:31:15.090 --> 00:31:17.050
We killed the curiosity
in most people.

00:31:17.050 --> 00:31:18.970
And so I'm really
arguing that education

00:31:18.970 --> 00:31:23.150
should be about
maximizing your curiosity

00:31:23.150 --> 00:31:25.430
so that you continue to
ask interesting questions

00:31:25.430 --> 00:31:28.360
for the rest of your life.

00:31:28.360 --> 00:31:31.650
